data.title: Midway, Utah, United States
data.text:
Midway, Utah, United States, is a town located in Wasatch County, known for its proximity to the Heber Valley Railroad and the Heber Valley Historic Railroad Museum. Situated at an elevation of 5,387 feet, Midway experiences a humid continental climate with warm summers and cold winters.
